# Trading Signal — project rules

Scoped rules live in `.cursor/rules/`:

| File | When it applies |
|------|-----------------|
| `core.mdc` | Always |
| `testing.mdc` | `*.test.ts`, `*.test.tsx`, `*_test.go`, `e2e/**` |
| `client.mdc` | `client/**` |
| `server.mdc` | `server/**` |

Stack: client (Vite/React), server (Express/Prisma + worker). Docker: `docker-compose.dev.yml` (local) or `docker-compose.prod.yml` (production builds).
